name: lw2-backend
description: - /user   - `GET` /     - Get user object for self     - ```json       { "token": "jwtToken" }       ```     - ```json       { "id": "uuid", "username": "username", "permissionLevel": 3, "email": "email@email.email", "name": "name" }       ```   - `PATCH` /     - Update self     - ```json       { "token": "jwtToken", ... }       ```     - ```json       { "id": "uuid", "username": "username", "permissionLevel": 3, "email": "email@email.email", "name": "name" }       ```   - `POST` /     - Create user     - ```json       { "username": "username", "pwHash": "hash", "email": "email@email.email", "name": "name" }        ```     - ```json       { "id": "uuid": "username": "username", "permissionLevel": 0, "email": "email@email.email", "name": "name" }       ```
